      {
        "level": 1,
        "name": "Gold Sink",
        "description": "<p>You gain the Deft Hands Perk (p. 68), and can take the Use Action to place nonmagical valuables into a container and close it. You can then open that container to replace the valuables with an Item of equal or lesser value to the valuables placed in it. This Item can't be a Relic or similar magic item.</p>",
        "statBonusPoints": 0,
        "extraTraining": 0,
        "requiredSpells": [],
